---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
	title="Setup"
	description="Learn how to set up GetCookie for your community or organization."
>
	<h1>Setup GetCookie</h1>
	<p class="lead">
		Get GetCookie running in your community or organization in just a few steps.
	</p>

	<div class="step">
		<div class="step-number">1</div>
		<div class="step-content">
			<h3>Add GetCookie to Discord</h3>
			<p>Click the "Add to Discord" button to invite the bot to your community.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="step">
		<div class="step-number">2</div>
		<div class="step-content">
			<h3>Configure Your Settings</h3>
			<p>Set up recognition channels and customize settings for your community or organization.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="step">
		<div class="step-number">3</div>
		<div class="step-content">
			<h3>Watch engagement happen</h3>
			<p>See how members recognize each other with Cookies and emojis and climb the leaderboards.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="callout">
		<p>
			<strong>💡 Need help?</strong> If you run into any issues during setup, check out our
			<a href="/docs/getting-started/need-help/">help page</a> for troubleshooting tips.
		</p>
	</div>
</DocsLayout>
